Author: bozo0142
Text: Thank you.. it’s honestly the scariest feeling; not knowing if you’ll ever be okay with yourself and fearing a life of this

Author: lyssland
Text: the secret of ED is that body dysmorphia will be there whether your BMI is 15 or your BMI is 45. there is no magical number to make you love yourself or to see yourself as "thin enough" and it sucks. it sucks so bad. i'm sorry you're struggling so much right now and i'm sending you love.
